The man goes home and makes the tea. He takes it to the woman but on the way he spills a bit on the floor. A cat comes by and drinks the tea. The man sits with the woman while she drinks her tea and he wonders how she is feeling. He is excited and nervous. He hopes he is not punished by the universe for casting this spell on the woman he loves. The woman seems to be feeling fine and he man wonders when she will first shapeshift and learn of her pow
